{
  "name": "RPlog_The_Capture_of_Han_Solo",
  "title": "The Capture of Han Solo",
  "summary": "In Capital City's Memorial Park on Etti IV, Chewbacca has been arrested by Corporate Sector Espos under a warrant issued by Dillon, watched over by VicePrex Piper and the Imperial agent Lady Alora. A disguised Han Solo infiltrates the scene posing as a ranting shopkeeper, attempting to spring the Wookiee, and a brawl erupts as Chewbacca sweeps the guards off their feet and flees with C3PO and Han. Alora pursues, using Han's choking and a hostage threat to force Chewbacca to drop him, and the Corellian is wounded by blaster fire and recaptured while the Wookiee and droid escape offworld. Han is dragged to the Port Security detention cell, where Alora tends his leg and conducts a barbed, flirtatious interrogation laced with references to his wife Leia and her ties to the Empire. Han gives nothing away, and Alora leaves him to Piper, departing to inform the Grand Moff of their prize catch.",
